Fix PotM South timing — thermal starts 7 AM not 10 AM

The trained weights had bestHours [10,11,12] causing "Be There by
10 AM" — but PotM South thermal regularly starts by 7-7:30 AM.

- bestHours updated to [7,8,9,10,11]
- Direction range in trained weights: 160-200 -> 110-250
- Speed range: 6-18 -> 5-20
- Headline now says "Flying NOW — Get Airborne!" when conditions
  are active (hour >= 7), not "Be There by 10 AM"
- Before 7 AM: "Thermal by 7 AM"
- Prediction window extended to currentHour <= 14 (was 12)
